{# Description: Raw copy/paste Jinja template for Spectra LS P3 metadata candidate payload parity validation. #}
{# Version: 2026.05.05.4 #}
{# Last updated: 2026-05-05 #}

{# =========================
  P3 Candidate Payload Parity Validation (MA Meta Candidates)
  Purpose: verify that state count, candidate rows, summary payload, and best-candidate payload are internally consistent.

  Expected healthy behavior:
    - state_count > 0 when rows/entities exist
    - row_count == summary_entities_count
    - best_entity is non-empty when best_score > 0
    - best_entity is contained in summary entities when summary has rows
  ========================= #}

{% set s_component = 'sensor.component_meta_candidates' %}
{% set s_legacy = 'sensor.ma_meta_candidates' %}
{% set s = s_component if states[s_component] is not none else s_legacy %}
{% set candidate_source = 'component_primary' if s == s_component else 'legacy_fallback' %}
{% set state_count = states(s) | int(0) %}
{% set state_obj = states[s] if states[s] is not none else none %}
{% set attrs = state_obj.attributes if state_obj is not none and state_obj.attributes is mapping else {} %}

{% set component_entities = attrs.entities if attrs.entities is defined and attrs.entities is sequence and attrs.entities is not string and attrs.entities is not mapping else [] %}
{% set component_names = attrs.names if attrs.names is defined and attrs.names is sequence and attrs.names is not string and attrs.names is not mapping else [] %}
{% set component_scores = attrs.scores if attrs.scores is defined and attrs.scores is sequence and attrs.scores is not string and attrs.scores is not mapping else [] %}

{% set rows_raw = state_attr(s, 'candidate_rows_json') | default([], true) %}
{% set rows = [] %}
{% if s == s_component %}
  {% set rows = component_entities %}
{% elif rows_raw is sequence and rows_raw is not string and rows_raw is not mapping %}
  {% set rows = rows_raw %}
{% elif rows_raw is mapping %}
  {% set mapped = (rows_raw.rows if rows_raw.rows is defined else (rows_raw.result if rows_raw.result is defined else [])) %}
  {% if mapped is sequence and mapped is not string and mapped is not mapping %}
    {% set rows = mapped %}
  {% endif %}
{% elif rows_raw is string %}
  {% set raw_trim = rows_raw | trim %}
  {% set raw_trim_l = raw_trim | lower %}
  {% if raw_trim_l not in ['unknown','unavailable','none',''] and (raw_trim.startswith('[') or raw_trim.startswith('{')) %}
    {% set parsed = raw_trim | from_json %}
    {% if parsed is sequence and parsed is not string and parsed is not mapping %}
      {% set rows = parsed %}
    {% elif parsed is mapping %}
      {% set mapped = (parsed.rows if parsed.rows is defined else (parsed.result if parsed.result is defined else [])) %}
      {% if mapped is sequence and mapped is not string and mapped is not mapping %}
        {% set rows = mapped %}
      {% endif %}
    {% endif %}
  {% endif %}
{% endif %}

{% set summary_raw = state_attr(s, 'candidate_summary_json') | default('{}', true) %}
{% if s == s_component %}
  {% set summary = {
    'entities': component_entities,
    'names': component_names,
    'scores': component_scores,
    'best_entity': state_attr(s, 'best_entity') | default('', true),
    'best_score': state_attr(s, 'best_score') | default(0, true)
  } %}
{% else %}
  {% set summary = summary_raw if (summary_raw is mapping) else ((summary_raw | from_json) if (summary_raw is string and (summary_raw | trim).startswith('{')) else {}) %}
{% endif %}
{% set summary_entities = (summary.entities if summary is mapping and summary.entities is defined else []) %}
{% set summary_best_entity = (summary.best_entity if summary is mapping and summary.best_entity is defined else '') %}
{% set summary_best_score = (summary.best_score if summary is mapping and summary.best_score is defined else 0) | float(0) %}

{% set best_raw = state_attr(s, 'best_candidate_json') | default('{}', true) %}
{% if s == s_component %}
  {% set best = {
    'entity': state_attr(s, 'best_entity') | default('', true),
    'score': state_attr(s, 'best_score') | default(0, true)
  } %}
{% else %}
  {% set best = best_raw if (best_raw is mapping) else ((best_raw | from_json) if (best_raw is string and (best_raw | trim).startswith('{')) else {}) %}
{% endif %}
{% set best_entity = (best.entity if best is mapping and best.entity is defined else '') %}
{% set best_score = (best.score if best is mapping and best.score is defined else 0) | float(0) %}

{% set row_count = rows | length %}
{% set summary_count = summary_entities | length %}

{% set count_matches_rows = ((state_count >= row_count) if s == s_component else (state_count == row_count)) %}
{% set rows_match_summary = (row_count == summary_count) %}
{% set best_pair_valid = (best_score == 0 and best_entity in ['', none]) or (best_score > 0 and best_entity not in ['', none]) %}
{% set summary_best_pair_valid = (summary_best_score == 0 and summary_best_entity in ['', none]) or (summary_best_score > 0 and summary_best_entity not in ['', none]) %}
{% set best_in_summary = (summary_count == 0 and best_entity in ['', none]) or (best_entity in summary_entities) %}

{% set ok_count = 0 %}
{% if count_matches_rows %}{% set ok_count = ok_count + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if rows_match_summary %}{% set ok_count = ok_count + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if best_pair_valid %}{% set ok_count = ok_count + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if summary_best_pair_valid %}{% set ok_count = ok_count + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if best_in_summary %}{% set ok_count = ok_count + 1 %}{% endif %}

{% set verdict = 'PASS' %}
{% if ok_count < 3 %}
  {% set verdict = 'FAIL' %}
{% elif ok_count < 5 %}
  {% set verdict = 'WARN' %}
{% endif %}

### P3 Candidate Payload Parity Validation (`sensor.component_meta_candidates` primary / `sensor.ma_meta_candidates` fallback)
- Result: **{{ verdict }}**
- Timestamp: **{{ now() }}**
- Gate score: **{{ ok_count }}/5**
- Effective source: **{{ candidate_source }}** (`{{ s }}`)

### Counts
- State count: **{{ state_count }}**
- Candidate rows count: **{{ row_count }}**
- Summary entities count: **{{ summary_count }}**

### Best-candidate surfaces
- `best_candidate_json`: **{{ {'entity': best_entity, 'score': best_score} | tojson }}**
- `summary.best_*`: **{{ {'entity': summary_best_entity, 'score': summary_best_score} | tojson }}**

### Checks
- State/count invariant valid: **{{ count_matches_rows }}** {% if s == s_component %}(component expects state_count >= row_count){% else %}(legacy expects equality){% endif %}
- Row count matches summary entities count: **{{ rows_match_summary }}**
- `best_candidate_json` pair valid: **{{ best_pair_valid }}**
- `summary.best_*` pair valid: **{{ summary_best_pair_valid }}**
- Best entity is in summary entities: **{{ best_in_summary }}**

### Debug payload snapshots
- `candidate_rows_json`: **{{ rows_raw }}**
- `candidate_summary_json` (or synthesized): **{{ summary_raw if s != s_component else summary | tojson }}**
- `best_candidate_json` (or synthesized): **{{ best_raw if s != s_component else best | tojson }}**

### Recommendation
{% if verdict == 'PASS' %}
- Candidate payload contract is internally consistent.
{% elif verdict == 'WARN' %}
- Candidate contract is partially consistent; review failed checks before relying on closeout gates.
{% else %}
- Candidate contract is inconsistent; do not rely on metadata closeout gates until fixed.
{% endif %}
